{"tid":2098823,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【TVB港姐初選】佳麗戰衣淘寶同款貨曝光 最平38蚊人仔 (蘋果日報 )","createTime":"2020-07-07T18:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T19:58:59.000Z","uid":360777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cc362c0d3bbbdfa74e36618d45170427b8be7184","tid":2098823,"uid":360777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T18:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又到一年一度香港小姐首輪面試，爭妍鬥豔，打扮得花枝招展，希望突圍而出！今早現身康城地鐵站，坐專車入TVB電視城，見她們均悉心打扮，雖然參加者未必淘寶買衫，不過淘寶卻有她們身穿的同款連身裙出售，價錢仲好平。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b59dd4558a1f50bbce44d6fdb2064ec5152e497","tid":2098823,"uid":326758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T18:59:18.000Z","msg":"哪兒來的勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee2271e61e533b509f5763dbdda1727a834bd0b","tid":2098823,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T19:58:59.000Z","msg":"蘋果啲記者咁得閒去搵款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}